#
- Beacon 的发射周期可调，比如苹果规定 100mS 发射一次，也就是说 100mS 里只发射 4ms, 
- iBeacon 协议并不用于传输定制化数据
- RSSI: Received Signal Strength Indication
- range: 70 meters - 10 inches
- vs Eddystone by Google
- BLE: Bluetooth Low Energy, Bluetooth 4.0 or Bluetooth Smart
- NFC range is up to 20 cm but the optimal range is < 4 cm
- estimote
- Gimbal Beacons, from Qualcomm, a product and a company
- 一个简单的测量精度(accurate/precision)结果： 在1m的距离标准差10cm，在8米的距离标准差2m
- 停留时间也是影响精度的一个很大因素，如果停留10s，精度会提高
- iOS device can be as a beacon with CBPeripheralManager

